The paper discusses Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) and proposes a Homomorphic Instruction Set Architecture (HISA) for developing FHE applications. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Programming Languages (cs.PL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the development of an end-to-end software stack, which could place it in the categories of Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Architecture (cs.AR).
